name: Maybe They Were in Front of us All Along....
description:
Very fleet of foot and hard to capture. Unicorns showed up in early Mesopotamian artworks. So, are they fantasy, fictional or myths, or with their transparent horns.... maybe they were in front of us all along....

This started out as a sketch that I drew at a local coffee shop. I took a picture of it and gave the sketch away to a lady next to us. I told her that I was going to turn it into an NFT, she had no idea what I was talking about. LOL

Anyway… a little back story. I hope you guys love it as much as I do!
